---
title: Creamy Ricotta & Pea Toasts with Arugula-Edamame Salad
description: It's official: peas and ricotta are the "it-combo" of the season. Move over asparagus. Mashed together and spread on hearty multigrain toasts, it's dangerously irresistible. A protein-rich salad of edamame, avocado, and peppery arugula make this a wonderfully light Spring dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5537b40e6ced6eae038b4567.jpg
